page_title: 'Quickstart - Get started using Provisioned Deployments with Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started provisioned deployments on Azure OpenAI Service.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free- Access granted to Azure OpenAI in the desired Azure subscription.    Currently, access to this service is by application. You can apply for access to Azure OpenAI Service by completing the form at https://aka.ms/oai/access.- Obtained Quota for a provisioned deployment and purchased a commitment. > [!NOTE]> Provisioned Throughput Units (PTU) are different from standard quota in Azure OpenAI and are not available by default. To learn more about this offering contact your Microsoft Account Team.
